  },
  {
    "content_id": 797942,
    "reference_id": 18462,
    "title": "約拿書 2:8–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32002008-32002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約拿這首詩篇式禱告的結尾與<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:16\">一章16節</a>相似：水手同樣因耶和華施行拯救的大能與憐憫的作為，而獻上祭物並許願。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32002008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 2:8",
          "end_ref": "32002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797943,
    "reference_id": 18463,
    "title": "約拿書 3:1–2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32003001-32003002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>本書下半部的開頭與上半部的開頭相同（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:1-Jonah1:2\">1:1–2</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 3:1",
          "end_ref": "32003002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 3:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797944,
    "reference_id": 18464,
    "title": "約拿書 3:1–4:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32003001-32004011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神再次吩咐約拿去向尼尼微宣講信息。這一次約拿順服了，結果出現了<span>出乎意料的情況</span>——尼尼微城如約拿所擔心的那樣悔改了，而他卻生了神的氣。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 3:1",
          "end_ref": "32004011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 4:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797946,
    "reference_id": 18466,
    "title": "約拿書 3:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32003003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>這是一座大城，需要三天才能走遍。神渴望拯救這座龐大的城市，而非毀滅它——城裡有許多人和牲畜（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:11\">4:11</a>）。然而，正是神的這份心意，令約拿抗拒（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">4:2</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:10-Jonah4:11\">10–11</a>）。</p></li><li><p>繞尼尼微城一圈約三英里，繞城一圈並不需三天。這裡的描述可能是指約拿將信息傳遍全城所需的時間，也可能包括城周圍的村莊。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32003003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 3:3",
          "end_ref": "32003003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 3:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797947,
    "reference_id": 18467,
    "title": "約拿書 3:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32003004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>再等四十日</span>，尼尼微<span>必傾覆了！</span>約拿的信息顯然沒有包含任何附帶條件——例如，「但如果你們悔改，神就不會毀滅你們」（請注意王在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:9\">3:9</a>中的不確定）。然而，約拿知道神渴望人悔改，而不是毀滅他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:10\">3:10</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">4:2</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32003004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 3:4",
          "end_ref": "32003004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 3:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797948,
    "reference_id": 18468,
    "title": "約拿書 3:5–6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32003005-32003006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>在這卷短書中，這是異教徒第二次對耶和華作出正面的回應（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:16\">1:16</a>）。</p></li><li><p>在古代以色列，禁食通常會伴隨著禱告和悔改，尤其是在困境之時（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:12\">撒下1:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:4\">尼1:4</a>）。穿上麻衣、坐在灰中，則常伴隨著哀悼與痛悔的悔改（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:34\">創37:34</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:15\">伯16:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:10\">哀2:10</a>）。亞述人顯然也有類似的習俗。這些舉動讓參與者能以具體的方式表達自己的悲傷，使眾人——包括神——都能看見。</p></li><li><p>尼尼微人的悔改，成了對耶穌時代那些心硬之人的控訴（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:41\">太12:41</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32003005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 3:5",
          "end_ref": "32003006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 3:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797949,
    "reference_id": 18469,
    "title": "約拿書 3:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32003006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>尼尼微的王，可能是這城的一位不知名的巡撫，也可能是亞述王，他或許經常以尼尼微作為政府所在地（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:9-2Kgs19:13\">王下19:9–13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32003006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 3:6",
          "end_ref": "32003006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 3:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797950,
    "reference_id": 18470,
    "title": "約拿書 3:7–8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32003007-32003008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>王將禁食與哀悼的儀式延伸到牲畜，藉此表明這場嚴重的危機，是需要停止一切日常運作，好讓人人都專心懇切禱告、並悔改、離棄惡行。其中，<span>強暴</span>——這已滲透他們整個社會——是首要之惡。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32003007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 3:7",
          "end_ref": "32003008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 3:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797945,
    "reference_id": 18465,
    "title": "約拿書 3:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32003010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>他改變了主意（和合本譯為：<span>他就後悔）</span>：若尼尼微人沒有悔改，神必毀滅他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:4\">3:4</a>）；但神早已預備好以憐憫來回應他們的悔改（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">4:2</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:11\">11</a>）。在神看來，這個轉變並非是在推翻祂原先的意圖，因為祂的心意本就包含施憐憫的可能性。這個轉變也不涉及神的預知問題。歷來教會都相信，神完全知道將來的事（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:4\">詩139:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:10\">賽46:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:28-Dan2:29\">但2:28–29</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:36\">太24:36</a>），而本段經文並沒有任何地方與此信念相矛盾。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32003010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 3:10",
          "end_ref": "32003010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 3:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797953,
    "reference_id": 18473,
    "title": "約拿書 4:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32004001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>此計劃的變更（字面意思是<em>它</em>；和合本譯為：<span>這事</span>）：請參見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"18465\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">三章10節的研讀註釋</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32004001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 4:1",
          "end_ref": "32004001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 4:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 18465,
          "content_id": 797945,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "約拿書 3:10",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797951,
    "reference_id": 18471,
    "title": "約拿書 4:1–7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32004001-32004007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>故事在此出現出人意料的轉折。約拿自己曾蒙受神的憐憫，卻對耶和華施予亞述人的憐憫心生抱怨。這位先知的頂撞反而更突顯出神的恩典（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:8-Jonah4:11\">4:8–11</a>中神的回應）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32004001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 4:1",
          "end_ref": "32004007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 4:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797954,
    "reference_id": 18474,
    "title": "約拿書 4:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32004002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>約拿表明自己當初逃避耶和華（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:3\">1:3</a>）的原因：他知道若尼尼微的惡人悔改，耶和華就不會毀滅他們。</p></li><li><p>我知道：約拿幾乎直接引用了<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:6-Exod34:7\">出埃及記三十四章6至7節</a>的內容，該段經文的背景是以色列與耶和華的立約關係。即使在舊約聖經時代，神的心意也是要將救恩傳到萬國（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:20\">太28:18–20</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32004002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 4:2",
          "end_ref": "32004002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 4:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797955,
    "reference_id": 18475,
    "title": "約拿書 4:3–5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32004003-32004005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約拿寧願死也不願順服神的旨意（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:8-Jonah4:9\">4:8–9</a>），並且願意等待，希望這城被毀滅（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:5\">4:5</a>）——這些都顯明了他的心硬，以及對亞述人的仇恨。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32004003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 4:3",
          "end_ref": "32004005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 4:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797956,
    "reference_id": 18476,
    "title": "約拿書 4:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32004004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華的回應是一個修辭性問句，其隱含的答案是：「不，當然不應該！」接下來的實例教訓（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:6-Jonah4:11\">4:6–11</a>）揭示了為什麼約拿不應該發怒。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32004004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 4:4",
          "end_ref": "32004004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 4:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797957,
    "reference_id": 18477,
    "title": "約拿書 4:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32004006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>耶和華是神與以色列立約時所用的名（例，見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:18\">詩72:18</a>）。神做這些事，是為了向約拿以及那些與他有同樣態度的以色列人，彰顯祂盟約之愛。</p></li><li><p>安排：見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"18449\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">約拿書一章17節的研讀註釋</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32004006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 4:6",
          "end_ref": "32004006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 4:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 18449,
          "content_id": 797929,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "約拿書 1:17",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797952,
    "reference_id": 18472,
    "title": "約拿書 4:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "32004011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>生活在屬靈黑暗中的人（和合本譯為：<span>其中不能分辨左手右手的......</span>人）：神憑著恩典，將祂藉先知所傳的真理之光帶入這座邪惡的城。不過，並非所有遇見神的光的人都有正面的回應（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:19-John3:21\">約3:19–21</a>）。但神樂意拯救那些真心悔改、憑信心領受祂話語的人。</p></li><li><p>本書在此戛然而止，讓讀者深思神向約拿提出的最後一個問題。神寧願拯救，也不願毀滅。那些已經蒙受祂憐憫的人，看見這同樣的憐憫臨到別人，應當歡喜快樂，哪怕是自己的仇敵。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "32004011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "JON 4:11",
          "end_ref": "32004011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "JON 4:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  }
]